요청하신 대로 로그인 화면에 **비밀번호 찾기** 링크를 추가했습니다. "아이디 저장" 체크박스 옆에 "비밀번호 찾기" 링크를 배치하여 기존 레이아웃을 유지하면서 기능을 추가했습니다.

아래 코드를 `aimakeui` 폴더 안에 있는 `loginform.html` 파일에 덮어쓰기 저장하시면 됩니다.

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>더죤환경기술(주) 기술진단팀 협업시스템 로그인</title>
    <style>
        /* Google Fonts - Noto Sans KR */
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@300;400;500;700&display=swap');

        :root {
            --primary-color: #007bff; /* Bright Blue */
            --primary-dark-color: #0056b3;
            --background-color: #f0f2f5; /* Light Gray Background */
            --card-background-color: #ffffff; /* White Card */
            --text-color: #333333; /* Dark Gray Text */
            --input-background-color: #f8f9fa; /* Very Light Gray Input */
            --input-border-color: #ced4da; /* Light Gray Border */
            --link-color: #007bff; /* Bright Blue Link */
            --button-hover-bg: #0069d9;
            --button-active-bg: #0056b3;
            --shadow-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--background-color);
            color: var(--text-color);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            line-height: 1.6;
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; /* Better font rendering */
            -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
        }

        .login-container {
            background-color: var(--card-background-color);
            padding: 30px; /* Reduced padding */
            border-radius: 10px; /* Slightly reduced border-radius */
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px var(--shadow-color); /* Lighter shadow */
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 380px; /* Reduced max-width */
            text-align: center;
            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; /* Subtle border */
            animation: fadeIn 0.6s ease-out; /* Slightly faster animation */
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-15px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        .login-header {
            margin-bottom: 25px; /* Reduced margin */
            color: var(--primary-color);
            font-size: 1.5em; /* Reduced font size */
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
            line-height: 1.3; /* Added line-height for better readability with <br> */
        }

        .input-group {
            margin-bottom: 15px; /* Reduced margin */
            text-align: left;
        }

        .input-group label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 6px; /* Reduced margin */
            color: var(--text-color);
            font-size: 0.9em; /* Reduced font size */
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .input-group input[type="text"],
        .input-group input[type="password"] {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px 12px; /* Reduced padding */
            border: 1px solid var(--input-border-color);
            border-radius: 6px; /* Reduced border-radius */
            background-color: var(--input-background-color);
            color: var(--text-color);
            font-size: 1em; /* Reduced font size */
            outline: none;
            transition: border-color 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }

        .input-group input[type="text"]:focus,
        .input-group input[type="password"]:focus {
            border-color: var(--primary-color);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(0, 123, 255, 0.25); /* Lighter focus shadow */
        }

        /* Placeholder styles */
        .input-group input::placeholder {
            color: #888;
            opacity: 0.8;
        }

        .options-group {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 25px; /* Reduced margin */
            font-size: 0.85em; /* Reduced font size */
        }
        
        /* New: Group for links on the right */
        .links-group {
            display: flex;
            gap: 15px; /* Space between links */
        }

        .remember-me {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .remember-me input[type="checkbox"] {
            margin-right: 6px; /* Reduced margin */
            width: 16px; /* Reduced size */
            height: 16px; /* Reduced size */
            accent-color: var(--primary-color);
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .remember-me label {
            color: var(--text-color);
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .action-link { /* Unified style for all action links */
            color: var(--link-color);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: color 0.3s ease, text-decoration 0.3s ease;
        }

        .action-link:hover {
            color: var(--primary-dark-color);
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        #loginButton {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 12px 18px; /* Reduced padding */
            background-color: var(--primary-color);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 6px; /* Reduced border-radius */
            font-size: 1.1em; /* Reduced font size */
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 3px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); /* Lighter shadow */
        }

        #loginButton:hover {
            background-color: var(--button-hover-bg);
            transform: translateY(-1px); /* More subtle hover effect */
        }

        #loginButton:active {
            background-color: var(--button-active-bg);
            transform: translateY(0);
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div id="loginContainer" class="login-container">
        <h2 id="loginHeader" class="login-header">더죤환경기술(주) 기술진단팀<br>협업시스템 로그인</h2>

        <form id="loginForm">
            <div class="input-group">
                <label for="usernameInput">아이디</label>
                <input type="text" id="usernameInput" placeholder="사용자 아이디를 입력하세요" required>
            </div>

            <div class="input-group">
                <label for="passwordInput">비밀번호</label>
                <input type="password" id="passwordInput" placeholder="비밀번호를 입력하세요" required>
            </div>

            <div class="options-group">
                <div class="remember-me">
                    <input type="checkbox" id="rememberMeCheckbox">
                    <label for="rememberMeCheckbox">아이디 저장</label>
                </div>
                <div class="links-group">
                    <a href="#" id="forgotPasswordLink" class="action-link">비밀번호 찾기</a>
                    <a href="registerform.html" id="registerLink" class="action-link">회원가입</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <button type="submit" id="loginButton">로그인</button>
        </form>
    </div>

    <script>
        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
            const loginForm = document.getElementById('loginForm');
            const usernameInput = document.getElementById('usernameInput');
            const passwordInput = document.getElementById('passwordInput');
            const rememberMeCheckbox = document.getElementById('rememberMeCheckbox');
            const registerLink = document.getElementById('registerLink');
            const forgotPasswordLink = document.getElementById('forgotPasswordLink'); // 새로운 링크 요소

            loginForm.addEventListener('submit', (event) => {
                event.preventDefault();

                const username = usernameInput.value;
                const password = passwordInput.value;
                const rememberMe = rememberMeCheckbox.checked;

                if (username === "" || password === "") {
                    alert("아이디와 비밀번호를 모두 입력해주세요.");
                    return;
                }

                alert(`
                    로그인 시도:
                    아이디: ${username}
                    비밀번호: ${password}
                    아이디 저장: ${rememberMe ? '예' : '아니오'}
                    (실제 로그인 처리는 백엔드에서 이루어집니다.)
                `);

                // 실제 C# (WebView2) 통신 예시:
                // if (window.chrome.webview) {
                //     window.chrome.webview.postMessage({ type: 'LOGIN', username, password, rememberMe });
                // }
            });

            // 회원가입 링크 클릭 이벤트 (registerform.html로 이동하도록 href 속성 설정)
            // registerLink.addEventListener('click', (event) => {
            //     event.preventDefault(); // 기본 동작을 막지 않고, href로 이동하도록 설정
            //     alert("회원가입 페이지로 이동합니다.");
            //     // if (window.chrome.webview) {
            //     //     window.chrome.webview.postMessage({ type: 'NAVIGATE', page: 'registerform.html' });
            //     // } else {
            //     //     window.location.href = "registerform.html";
            //     // }
            // });

            // 비밀번호 찾기 링크 클릭 이벤트
            forgotPasswordLink.addEventListener('click', (event) => {
                event.preventDefault();
                alert("비밀번호 찾기 페이지로 이동합니다. (실제 페이지는 구현이 필요합니다.)");
                // 실제 C# (WebView2) 통신 예시:
                // if (window.chrome.webview) {
                //     window.chrome.webview.postMessage({ type: 'NAVIGATE', page: 'forgot_password.html' });
                // }
            });

            // 아이디 저장 기능 (LocalStorage 예시 - 필요 시 주석 해제하여 사용)
            // if (localStorage.getItem('savedUsername')) {
            //     usernameInput.value = localStorage.getItem('savedUsername');
            //     rememberMeCheckbox.checked = true;
            // }

            // rememberMeCheckbox.addEventListener('change', () => {
            //     if (rememberMeCheckbox.checked) {
            //         localStorage.setItem('savedUsername', usernameInput.value);
            //     } else {
            //         localStorage.removeItem('savedUsername');
            //     }
            // });
            // usernameInput.addEventListener('input', () => {
            //     if (rememberMeCheckbox.checked) {
            //         localStorage.setItem('savedUsername', usernameInput.value);
            //     }
            // });
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
```